{"title":"Nginx部署","uid":"22e976045f79a913a7ea0143ddb4fa7e","slug":"Nginx部署","date":"2023-04-04T06:45:10.363Z","updated":"2023-04-04T08:16:00.635Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Nginx部署.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/medias/1668057368202.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"nginx源码\"><a href=\"#nginx源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"nginx源码\"></a>nginx源码</h2><p><strong>官网：</strong><a href=\"http://nginx.org/\">nginx news</a></p>\n<p><strong>源码包：</strong></p>\n<!--下载想要的nginx版本-->\n\n<p><img src=\"../images/image-20230404145154624.png\" alt=\"image-20230404145154624\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-源码包下载：\"><a href=\"#1-源码包下载：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.源码包下载：\"></a><strong>1.源码包下载：</strong></h3><!--复制源码包的下载链接-->\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">wget http:&#x2F;&#x2F;nginx.org&#x2F;download&#x2F;nginx-x.x.x.tar.gz -P &#x2F;usr&#x2F;src\ncd &#x2F;usr&#x2F;src\nls</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"2-安装依赖包-解压源码\"><a href=\"#2-安装依赖包-解压源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.安装依赖包,解压源码\"></a>2.安装依赖包,解压源码</h3><p><strong>#centos</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum -y install gcc pcre-devel zlib-devel</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>gcc： 源码编译工具 </li>\n<li>pcre-devel： nginx url_rewrite 功能提供包 </li>\n<li>zlib-devel： nginx 压缩功能提供包</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>#ubuntu</strong>   <!--自动安装依赖包--></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo apt-get -f install</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">tar -xvf 包名\ncd 包文件夹</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"3-配置nginx源码\"><a href=\"#3-配置nginx源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.配置nginx源码\"></a>3.配置nginx源码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">.&#x2F;configure --prefix&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx</code></pre>\n\n<!--配置目的：--> \n\n<!--1）检查环境 是否 满足安装条件 依赖解决--> \n\n<!--2）指定安装方式 配置文件 命令文件 各种文件放哪里 开启模块功能【内置模块 三方模块】--> \n\n<!--3）指定软件安装在那里-->\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"4编译、安装-nginx-源码\"><a href=\"#4编译、安装-nginx-源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4编译、安装 nginx 源码\"></a>4编译、安装 nginx 源码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">make &amp;&amp; make install</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"5-启动nginx\"><a href=\"#5-启动nginx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.启动nginx\"></a>5.启动nginx</h3><p><strong>检查配置文件</strong>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx -t</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Nginx启动：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Nginx关闭：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">killall –s QUIT nginx</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>指定配置文件：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx -c &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;conf&#x2F;nginx.conf</code></pre>\n\n<!--注意：-c 指定配置文件的路径，不加的话，nginx会自动加载默认路径的配置文件，可以通过 -h查看帮助命令-->\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"6-查看nginx进程\"><a href=\"#6-查看nginx进程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.查看nginx进程\"></a>6.查看nginx进程</h3><p>使用 netstat 命令查看启动端口 </p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">netstat -ano | grep 80</code></pre>\n\n<p>使用losf命令查看启动端口</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">lsof -i :80</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"7-创建链接\"><a href=\"#7-创建链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7.创建链接\"></a>7.创建链接</h3> <!--建立软链接（由于/usr/local/bin包含于$PATH当中，这样就不需要额外的设置环境变量了，这意味着可以在其他路径下直接运行nginx命令）-->\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ln -s &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;bin</code></pre>\n\n","feature":true,"text":"nginx源码官网：nginx news 源码包： 1.源码包下载： wget http:&#x2F;&#x2F;nginx.org&#x2F;download&#x2F;nginx-x.x.x.tar.gz -P &#x2F;usr&#x2F;src cd &#x2F;usr&...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":974,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":4,"path":"api/categories/linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LNMP+N","slug":"LNMP-N","count":1,"path":"api/tags/LNMP-N.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#nginx%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">nginx源码</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81%E5%8C%85%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.源码包下载：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E5%8C%85-%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.安装依赖包,解压源码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEnginx%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.配置nginx源码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-nginx-%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4编译、安装 nginx 源码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5-%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8nginx\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5.启动nginx</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#6-%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8Bnginx%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">6.查看nginx进程</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#7-%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">7.创建链接</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{